    <defName>Apparel_AnimalFlakArmor</defName>
    <label>animal flak armor</label>
    <description>A tough fabric animal jacket with armor plates sewn in. While it's not as good as solid armor, it offers effective protection against all manner of attacks while remaining quite comfortable.\nCurrently wearable by:\nAlpaca, Husky, Labrador Retriever</description>
